00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:25.000
Coach Alex:  Exactly.  And when you see a student who's off task, try using proximity control.  Just move closer to them and continue teaching.  Often, that's all it takes to get them back on track.

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:40.000
