00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:25.000
Coach Alex:  You could smile at them, give them a quick nod of encouragement, or even ask them a question about the lesson.  It shows that you're paying attention to them and that you care about their learning.

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:40.000
